msgctxt "0001"
msgid "Not at all!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0002"
msgid "Absolutely!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0003"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Let's talk about <CLT><CLT 3>reloading<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0004"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Starting with this next Bullet Time Battle, we're\n"
"gonna add one more ingredient to the recipe.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0005"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>On the bottom of the screen, underneath the Tempo\n"
"Marker, you'll see your <CLT><CLT 3>ammo count<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0006"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Up until now, there hasn't really been a limit on how\n"
"you destroy your opponent's statements.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0007"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>But from now on, just locking on and pressing the\n"
"%CTRL_BULLET_TIME_ATTACK% won't be enough to handle them.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0008"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Now it will cost you \n"
"<CLT><CLT 3>one bullet<CLT><CLT 23> to <CLT><CLT 3>destroy a single remark<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0009"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Once you run out of bullets, you can't destroy any\n"
"more statements, no matter how locked on you are.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0010"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>However, you can <CLT><CLT 3>reload<CLT><CLT 23> by pressing the <CLT><CLT 3>%CTRL_BULLET_TIME_RELOAD%<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0011"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>…\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0012"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Just like locking on, you'll have to press \n"
"the <CLT><CLT 3>%CTRL_BULLET_TIME_RELOAD%<CLT><CLT 23> in time with the Tempo Marker.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0013"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>…\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0014"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Basically, just remember that the <CLT><CLT 3>%CTRL_BULLET_TIME_RELOAD%<CLT><CLT 23> now\n"
"has a function along with the %CTRL_BULLET_TIME_BUTTONS% buttons.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0015"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>You will <CLT><CLT 3>automatically reload<CLT><CLT 23> at the start of <CLT><CLT 3>Fever Time<CLT><CLT 23>, \n"
"and your ammo <CLT><CLT 3>will not decrease<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0016"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Oh, but if your action difficulty is set to Gentle,\n"
"you won't have to reload at all.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0017"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>In which case, you can ignore everything I just said!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0018"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Well then...good luck, and have fun!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0019"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>A <CLT><CLT 3>new element has been added<CLT><CLT 23> to Bullet Time Battles.\n"
"Would you like to hear more?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
